55:24.750 --> 55:26.625
EMILY: Help me!
Help me! Help me!

55:26.709 --> 55:28.291
Charlie!

55:29.083 --> 55:31.041
Please.
Please don't do this!

55:31.125 --> 55:32.834
Please don't do this!

55:32.917 --> 55:35.041
-Charlie!
-POLICEMAN: Get back.

55:35.625 --> 55:38.083
(CROWD CLAMORS LOUDLY)

55:38.166 --> 55:41.125
EMILY: Please.
Give me one minute.

55:43.083 --> 55:44.959
Charlie!

55:46.500 --> 55:50.083
(CROWD CONTINUES CLAMORING)

55:55.875 --> 55:59.083
EMILY: Charlie!
Please don't do this.

56:00.208 --> 56:01.458
Please.

56:02.000 --> 56:03.250
Charlie!

56:04.250 --> 56:07.500
Please, don't do this!
Please, don't!

56:07.583 --> 56:09.625
My baby.

56:09.709 --> 56:13.250
(SOBBING)

56:21.291 --> 56:24.750
(INAUDIBLE)

