with a church choir housewife

57:14.583 --> 57:17.834
part of a kidnapping
ring out of Milwaukee?

57:17.917 --> 57:20.333
Can't see that holding,
even if she did do it.

57:20.959 --> 57:23.542
(LAUGHTER)

57:24.291 --> 57:25.583
(E.B. SIGHS)

57:25.667 --> 57:28.875
He thinks
I'm last night's eggs.

57:28.959 --> 57:32.834
Thinks he's playing me.
You watch.

57:32.917 --> 57:35.166
We're gonna run him over
like a streetcar.

57:36.959 --> 57:39.625
They shoulda let her
see the kid get buried.

57:39.709 --> 57:41.125
E.B.: Oh, they said they would.

57:41.208 --> 57:42.875
But who tells the truth
anymore?

57:48.500 --> 57:49.667
I don't like it here.

57:53.417 --> 57:54.834
We do what we don't like

57:54.917 --> 57:57.208
