in a heartbeat.

1:05:44.709 --> 1:05:46.333
JONATHAN:
Detectives don't play fair.

1:05:46.625 --> 1:05:48.041
PERRY MASON:
I got a bunch of your reports.

1:05:48.291 --> 1:05:50.291
