that kidnapping write-up.

1:05:50.375 --> 1:05:51.333
Open that door!

1:05:51.417 --> 1:05:52.709
You saw something
and you know it.

1:05:52.792 --> 1:05:53.792
-Detectives!
-(GRUNTS)

